        <p>Architect & Engineer dsjhgfjd gfjhdaj gdfjhg jdfg ljdfgjlhdf ghlfkjg dfhj jdhsgfjksdg jfdsgjfhg dsjhfg jsds  ddds dsg </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  <% end %>

</div>

<style>
.card {
    box-shadow: 0 4px 8px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.2);
    transition: 0.3s;
    width: 40%;
}

.card:hover {
